## Quick Start

### 1. Configure Database

Edit `config/database.cfc` with your database credentials.

### 2. Run Migrations

```bash
lucli migrate
```

### 3. Start Development Server

```bash
lucli server start
```

Your application will be available at `http://localhost:8080`

